# Rock Paper Scissors Game

## Languages used:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
  
## About The Project:
- A simple javascript rock paper scissors game.
- The computer picks a random move built on a simple if-else statement block.
- The code compares the player and computer moves, decides the result, and gives the score accordingly.
- Displays and maintains game scores.
- Integrated localStorage to save the scores on the computer system and resets only when the reset button is clicked.
- In-built object DOM is used to Display the results on the game screen.
- Added an Auto Play Feature where the computer plays against itself every second and displays results. 

